This is cloned from sourceforge to store an old modification I made to this code during my PhD. Starting from 3.11, I added Lambert equal area projection and cubehelix colour scheme. See feature/lambert_equal_area for these changes.

Original readme:

HEALPix 

Hierarchical Equal Area isoLatitude Pixelation of the sphere

For information on HEALPix visit
https://healpix.sourceforge.io

For information on installation of HEALPix packages
see INSTALL
or type
 healpix_doc


